1. *Njegovim* roditeljima se svide njegovi postignući. (His parents are proud of his achievements.) 
2. *Njegovim* odlukama je obilježio svoje vrijeme. (He marked his time with his decisions.)
3. *Njegovim* velikim trudom je postigao uspjeh. (He achieved success with his hard work.)
4. *Njegovim* prijateljima je bio uzor. (He was an example to his friends.)
5. *Njegovim* očevima je bio uzor. (He was an example to his fathers.) 
6. *Njegovim* uspjesima je obilježio vrijeme. (He marked the time with his successes.)